formation from different\nsources as a major barrier to information processing. The results of this study\nindicate a need for authentic, consistent, and individualized information for\ntype 2 diabetics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Oct 2019 04:59:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-29"}
