ting. Co and Ni doping causes further departure\nfrom nesting, which accompanies the reduction of critical temperature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Oct 2019 10:15:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-29"}
