escing flux ropes. The latter were recently\nstudied in two-way coupled kinetic-fluid models, where the complete phase-space\ninformation of reconnection is incorporated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 28 Oct 2019 13:24:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-29"}
